latestPosts.caption:
@virdas made history as the first Indian to host the @iemmys - a massive win in itself. But there’s a little story behind the scenes that I’d love to share.

When he shared his vision of launching a new designer at the Emmy’s by giving them a platform, I knew this project would be unforgettable. It was unconventional, bold, a little daunting, and certainly nerve-wracking, but above it all it was exhilarating. And that’s just the magic of working with him - he is always pushing boundaries.

After sifting through countless entries, we found @thegirlwhostitched from Delhi, whose vision struck a chord with us. The goal was never about making a bold fashion statement, it was about staying true to who Vir is while giving a talented designer the spotlight they deserve. On that stage, he didn’t just look like himself, he was himself. And that’s all that mattered to me when I had to bring it all together. 

He’s wearing @salookalife by @thegirlwhostitched and jewels by @hanut101 

That’s @virdas for you, at the @iemmys 2024 💫

Vir Das, Emmy’s, Styling, Men’s Fashion, Celebrity Style

#virdas #emmys #mensfashion #india #celebstyle
